com.gracehoppers.jlovas.bookwrm

Class Trade

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gracehoppers.jlovas.bookwrm.Trade

  • public class Trade
extends java.lang.Object
    Trade is a class that represents a trade between a borrower and an owner. Contains Booleans accpted and declined, an instance of the TradeStatus, an owner's book and a list of the borrower's books. As well as both the owner and the borrower accounts, and a string of comments on the trade. Getters and Setters for these fields.
    See Also:
    Account, TradeStatus, Book, TradeCompletion
